      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JET BOOTS TOMMY (2) broke a two start winning streak with a minor placing (30.43) last time at Wentworth Park. Solid record at the distance winning five races. On top here on best form and expected to feature. SNACKS (1) drifted back settling but did best work late to finish 4th at Taree Super Track over 300m (18.09). Can do much better this time. CHLOE'S COMET (7) jumped cleanly from the rails to lead much the way when second (22.95) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Has performed well from this box with a win and nine minor placings to her name from 15 starts. Will give a great sight again. KANGAROO JACK (6) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
